com.novell.ldapchai.cr
Interface ChallengeSet

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ChaiChallengeSet
public interface ChallengeSet
extends Serializable

An instance of a challenge set to be used for challenge/response. Instances of ChallengeSet can be created or read using ChaiCrFactory.

Author:
Jason D. Rivard

int minimumResponses()

isLocked

boolean isLocked()
Check to see if any of the underlying challenges are not locked. If any challenge is not locked, then the entire ChallengeSet is considered to be not locked.

Returns:
true if all contained Challenges are locked.
